<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reaktivasi Akun {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f2f4f8;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1f2937;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);
        }
        .header {
            padding: 24px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #ec4899 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .brand {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 28px;
        }
        .title {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .cta-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #7c3aed;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .link-box {
            margin: 12px 0 20px;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #334155;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .notice {
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0 0 12px;
        }
        .notice.warning {
            background-color: #fff7ed;
            border: 1px solid #fdba74;
            color: #9a3412;
        }
        .notice.info {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #7dd3fc;
            color: #0c4a6e;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 0 28px 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="header">
                <p class="brand">{{companyName}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h1 class="title">Reaktivasi Akun</h1>

                <p>Halo {{name}},</p>
                <p>Kami menerima permintaan untuk mengaktifkan kembali akun Anda.</p>

                <div class="cta-wrap">
                    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Reaktivasi Akun</a>
                </div>

                <p>Jika tombol tidak berfungsi, salin dan buka tautan berikut:</p>
                <div class="link-box">{{verificationUrl}}</div>

                <div class="notice warning">Tautan reaktivasi ini berlaku selama <strong>{{expiresIn}}</strong>.</div>
                <div class="notice info">Jika Anda tidak meminta reaktivasi akun, abaikan email ini atau hubungi support kami.</div>

                <p>Salam,<br>Tim {{companyName}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>© {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>Email ini dikirim otomatis, mohon tidak membalas.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
